Doctor is very friendly and helpful throughout the treatment. 

Less waiting time, explains the issue and the treatment procedures very well.

I had unbearable wisdom tooth pain during lockdown. Came across Dr Jigna’s profile on Practo. I called her and as advised shared the picture of my tooth. She recommended anti biotics and pain killers but because the tooth needed an extraction and her clinic was still closed , she suggested another doctor whose clinic was open and this was only to help me get  rid of the dreadful pain. I finally got the tooth extracted. Thank you Dr Jigna!!!! You’ve been so helpful during this difficult time, More so very humble * ***** * ***** ****** ***

It was a great experience! Dr. Jigna is fast with the work, made me very comfortable and treated any questions that I had with respect and was quick to describe the issues at hand. She is also very accommodating and understanding as my schedule is very erratic and I had to cancel multiple appointments. 

The anterior filling she’s done is fantastic and gels in well with my teeth - which was not the case with my earlier dentist. The experience was very satisfactory and I will be returning (hopefully only for cleanings and not any more fillings!)

Good centre for all dental treatment .
Extra care is taken to ensure patient is comfortable.Good followup with patient by staff of the clinic.
the whole experience was really nice, the doctor is friendly and was completely satisfied with the results

Great experience as a first timer.I especially loved how Dr.Jigna Kanavia really took her time to explain my treatment options. The doctor's demeanor has really put me at ease so I highly recommend this clinic.

Doctor is very friendly.she is very confident and quick with her work.location is very easy to find.very pleasant atmosphere of the clinic.staff is very polite.she makes the patient very comfortable and explains everything before starting treatment.recommend this dentist.

********* ******* *** *** **** * **** ******* ** ***.The endeavor is to solve the issue with long term dental health.The doctor was in touch with me throughout the treatment and also post my wisdom tooth extraction.such personalised care is very rare in the city.highly recommended.

I have been visiting since a while now. Even though I have now shifted to New Mumbai, I make a point of visiting Dr. Jigna only for my annual checkups and dental issues. She is very friendly and awesome with her work and makes nervous patients like me so comfortable that I don't mind the 2 hours of travel to visit her clinic.Overall very good and pleasant experience. Highly recommend her to all.

It has been such a smooth process from start to end with Dr. Jigna, both in terms of communication and the treatment process itself. The doctor, as well as the staff were really helpful and kind throughout, from checking in about patient's well being even after the sessions are over, to co-ordinating follow ups keeping our convenience in mind, this kind of empathetic approach sticks out immediately. Highly recommended!
